step 1:  create the manifest for the java Jar file

step 2: from command line run -> jar cfm DoorBellRings.jar manifest.txt *.class 
	--> this creates the jar file
	--> test the jar file by running : java -jar DoorBellRings.jar

step 3: create the Dockerfile
	--> leave empty space at the end of the file

step 4: run in command line -> docker build -t doorbellrings .
	--> this builds the docker image

step 5: check the images -> docker image ls

step 6: run the docker image -> docker run /doorbellrings
